{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/2019/06/19/game-oan-tu-ti-su-dung-danh-sach-lien-ket","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"d766e1db-5efc-5ad4-9211-e83fa0b37219","html":"<h1 id=\"game-oẳn-tù-tì-sử-dụng-danh-sách-liên-kết-\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#game-o%E1%BA%B3n-t%C3%B9-t%C3%AC-s%E1%BB%AD-d%E1%BB%A5ng-danh-s%C3%A1ch-li%C3%AAn-k%E1%BA%BFt-\" aria-label=\"game oẳn tù tì sử dụng danh sách liên kết  permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Game oẳn tù tì sử dụng danh sách liên kết ?</h1>\n<p>Chào các bạn, lại là mình đây.\nChắc các bạn cũng đã từng viết một game đơn giản như oẳn tù tì rồi đúng không nhỉ.\nMình đã tham khảo nhiểu bài viết trên mạng nhưng thuật toán kiểm tra khá là dài</p>\n<h2 id=\"thuật-toán\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#thu%E1%BA%ADt-to%C3%A1n\" aria-label=\"thuật toán permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Thuật toán</h2>\n<p>Hôm nay mình sẽ hướng dẫn các bạn một thuật toán khác cũng dài không kém nhưng khá thú vị, đấy là sử dụng danh sách liên kết (vòng đơn):</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/qaqncbs.png\" alt=\"Mô tả thuật toán\"></p>\n<p>Ý tưởng ở đây là:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Các node có giá trị lần lượt là 1, 2, 3 tương đương với BAO , BÚA , KÉO</li>\n<li>Node phía trước sẽ trỏ tới node phía sau theo thứ tự BAO > BÚA > KÉO > BAO</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"các-bước-thực-hiện\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#c%C3%A1c-b%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bc-th%E1%BB%B1c-hi%E1%BB%87n\" aria-label=\"các bước thực hiện permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Các bước thực hiện</h2>\n<h3 id=\"khởi-tạo-danh-sách-liên-kết\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#kh%E1%BB%9Fi-t%E1%BA%A1o-danh-s%C3%A1ch-li%C3%AAn-k%E1%BA%BFt\" aria-label=\"khởi tạo danh sách liên kết permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Khởi tạo danh sách liên kết</h3>\n<p>Ở đây mình sử dụng danh sách liên kết vòng đơn nên khai báo như sau:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"c\"><pre class=\"language-c\"><code class=\"language-c\"><span class=\"token macro property\"><span class=\"token directive-hash\">#</span><span class=\"token directive keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"token string\">&lt;stdio.h></span></span>\n<span class=\"token macro property\"><span class=\"token directive-hash\">#</span><span class=\"token directive keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"token string\">&lt;stdlib.h></span></span>\n<span class=\"token macro property\"><span class=\"token directive-hash\">#</span><span class=\"token directive keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"token string\">&lt;conio.h></span></span>\n<span class=\"token macro property\"><span class=\"token directive-hash\">#</span><span class=\"token directive keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"token string\">&lt;time.h></span></span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 1- bua : 2-keo: 3-bao</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">struct</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Node</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n <span class=\"token comment\">//  struct Node *prev;</span>\n   <span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> data<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n   <span class=\"token keyword\">struct</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Node</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span>next<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">typedef</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">struct</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Node</span> Node<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nNode <span class=\"token operator\">*</span>pHead<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span>pTail<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"token function\">init</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">srand</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token function\">time</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token constant\">NULL</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token comment\">//Khoi tao seed cho ham rand</span>\n    pHead <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>Node <span class=\"token operator\">*</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token function\">malloc</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">sizeof</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>Node<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token comment\">//Bua</span>\n    pHead<span class=\"token operator\">-></span>data <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    pHead<span class=\"token operator\">-></span>next <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>Node <span class=\"token operator\">*</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token function\">malloc</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">sizeof</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>Node<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token comment\">//Keo</span>\n    pHead<span class=\"token operator\">-></span>next<span class=\"token operator\">-></span>data <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    pTail <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> pHead<span class=\"token operator\">-></span>next<span class=\"token operator\">-></span>next <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>Node <span class=\"token operator\">*</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token function\">malloc</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">sizeof</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>Node<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token comment\">//Bao</span>\n    pTail<span class=\"token operator\">-></span>data <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    pTail<span class=\"token operator\">-></span>next <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> pHead<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token comment\">//tro ve Head</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"viết-hàm-chọn-cho-máy\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#vi%E1%BA%BFt-h%C3%A0m-ch%E1%BB%8Dn-cho-m%C3%A1y\" aria-label=\"viết hàm chọn cho máy permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Viết hàm chọn cho máy</h3>\n<p>Cái này rất đơn giản. Chỉ cần viết hàm random từ 1 đến 3.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"c\"><pre class=\"language-c\"><code class=\"language-c\"><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> <span class=\"token function\">computerChoose</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token function\">rand</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">%</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">//random 1-3</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"viết-hàm-showmenu-và-showchoose\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#vi%E1%BA%BFt-h%C3%A0m-showmenu-v%C3%A0-showchoose\" aria-label=\"viết hàm showmenu và showchoose permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Viết hàm showMenu và showChoose</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>hàm showMenu để hiển thị menu.</li>\n<li>hàm showChoose để chuyển 1-2-3 về BÚA, KÉO, BAO.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"c\"><pre class=\"language-c\"><code class=\"language-c\"><span class=\"token keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"token function\">showMenu</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">system</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"cls\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token comment\">//xóa màn hình</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">printf</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"GAME OAN TU TI:\\n\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">printf</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"1. Bua \\n\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">printf</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"2. Keo \\n\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">printf</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"3. Bao \\n\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"token function\">showChoose</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> value<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">switch</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>value<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">case</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n            <span class=\"token function\">printf</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"BUA\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n            <span class=\"token keyword\">break</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">case</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n            <span class=\"token function\">printf</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"KEO\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n            <span class=\"token keyword\">break</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">case</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n            <span class=\"token function\">printf</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"BAO\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n            <span class=\"token keyword\">break</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"viết-hàm-tìm-kiếm-node-chứa-lựa-chọn\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#vi%E1%BA%BFt-h%C3%A0m-t%C3%ACm-ki%E1%BA%BFm-node-ch%E1%BB%A9a-l%E1%BB%B1a-ch%E1%BB%8Dn\" aria-label=\"viết hàm tìm kiếm node chứa lựa chọn permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Viết hàm tìm kiếm node chứa lựa chọn</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"c\"